Description:
You see in the distance a flagless ship chasing a big white whale. They seem to be in the process of hunting the creature.

Whales, besides being majestic animals, are revered by the people of these islands, so not even the COT dares to hunt them.

The white whale is struggling with its chasers and is fleeing in your direction, faster than you expected.
